platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Years into transforming the workplace, Slack continues to be as essential to teams as ever. Chatting with your colleagues in dedicated channels is at the core of this productivity powerhouse, but dont snooze on its direct messaging tools, app integrations, and world-famous emoji support. If you need to gather the team for that one final push, youll want to do it in Slack.

This productivity powerhouse is as essential to teams as ever. Chat in dedicated channels or direct messages, get things done with app integrations and make a statement thanks to top-class emoji support.
